&lt;p&gt;Warrington and Halton Hospitals Occupational Health &amp; Wellbeing service has an exciting opportunity for a Receptionist / Clerical Assistant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a personable, enthusiastic and motivated individual, who has excellent communication and computer skills. The applicant must have a flexible approach to work, supporting other administration colleagues. The contract is 15 hours per week; this will be over 2 or 3 days in line with departmental needs.&lt;/p&gt;
